{"tid":1095662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「六四紀念館」遭惡意破壞 支聯會：不會被嚇倒 誓4.26重開","createTime":"2019-04-07T07:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T08:43:32.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"353afa23aa69efd8095a74aa103bbcd23b11cc7f","tid":1095662,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQzC1F8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQzC1F8.png&h=7619cd39&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YVwRmGb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYVwRmGb.png&h=74352ae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地上遺下鹽水痕迹。受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0hP7EsT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0hP7EsT.png&h=8afe3b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dOR9SNU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdOR9SNU.png&h=fd7d511c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AjLR57Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAjLR57Z.png&h=d5ee83c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rxu3XeF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frxu3XeF.png&h=9d717603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年是六四30周年，支聯會幾經努力，早前終於購得位於旺角一單位，計劃於本月26日重開「六四紀念館」，歡迎學校、團體及各界人士參觀。惟今早（7日）10時左右，工作人員返回紀念館工作時，發現大門鐵閘被打開，鐵門鎖頭不翼而飛，牆身的10個插座、總電掣和總電掣箱更被鹽水淋濕，明顯遭惡意破壞，打壓紀念館重開。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會強調不會被嚇倒，將加強保安，爭取在本月26日重開紀念館，毋忘六四，與港人一起紀念八九民運30周年。同時，支聯會已為此報警，希望警方早日將惡意破壞人士繩之於法。據知，支聯會此前未有收到任何恐嚇信件等，但因該館尚未開放，暫未安裝閉路電視。"},{"pid":"90080128d2eb5a959fc7ce91c0971fe8e3ae55fd","tid":1095662,"uid":26451,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f669bd95c0d214d052d709468daa1b30ad190369","tid":1095662,"uid":237562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:36:37.000Z","msg":"自己做㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321a165a67946a2ad31b257d2f4531d5a0fb3e46","tid":1095662,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"有冇裝cam?"},{"pid":"0b6062db9c0538ef084e146645919dc01b9cf962","tid":1095662,"uid":147047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:37:47.000Z","msg":"藍屍=黑社會"},{"pid":"cf9c972503e2dcf9078e72cbde2baaf225ba74e2","tid":1095662,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T08:13:14.000Z","msg":"426<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283f903b9e741ca6a6a24722fcebe5c3f2591012","tid":1095662,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"321a165a67946a2ad31b257d2f4531d5a0fb3e46","tid":1095662,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"有冇裝cam?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T08:42:21.000Z","msg":"重點，泛民俾人搞嘅事，宜家我唔敢跟車太貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我支持佢好好開個紀念館，但唔好太浪費錢"},{"pid":"7e9a35ecb67af8a6e2762d2d694e9ce1988161dc","tid":1095662,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"321a165a67946a2ad31b257d2f4531d5a0fb3e46","tid":1095662,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"有冇裝cam?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T08:43:32.000Z","msg":"但因該館尚未開放，暫未安裝閉路電視。<br />\n呢個時代都冇老閉?"}]}